node.text: @horusstraps is currently offering 35% off their entire site with code "SUMMER35"

The @jacobandco x @alecmonopoly Collaboration Timepiece Is Here! The Astronomia Alec Monopoly and it is a true work of art.

This piece contains miniature pop characters and images that are staples of Monopoly’s artwork within the iconic Astronomia four-arm vertical movement and its exclusive complications. 

When @jacobandco teams up with a world renown artist such as Alec Monopoly together they make a masterpiece showing why they are the most creative watch company in the industry.

The Astronomia Alec Monopoly is limite to only 9 pieces and retails for $600,000

node.text:
@jacobandco has created the perfect luxury watch for any workd traveller, the jaw dropping EPIC SF24 TOURBILLON

With its groundbreaking city-time display, the Epic SF24 Tourbillon enters a bold new dimension entirely undiscovered by traditional watches. Named after its Split-Flap, 24-city, vertical second time zone display, the Epic SF24 Tourbillon is a jet-set world-traveler's watch that is unique in its complexity and utility. Remarkably challenging to engineer and manufacture, yet easy and intuitive to use: the functionality and design of the Epic SF24 render it prepared to take on the world.
